---
import Layout from "../layouts/BlogPost.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="About THHT (thôt)"
  description="A bit about Thinking Hard / Hardly Thinking and the person behind it."
  pubDate={new Date()}
>
  <style>
    .contact-intro {
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .contact-form {
      display: grid;
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }

    .contact-row {
      display: grid;
      gap: 1rem;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }

    .contact-field {
      display: grid;
      gap: 0.4rem;
    }

    .contact-field label {
      font-family: var(--font-sans);
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      color: var(--ink);
    }

    .contact-field input,
    .contact-field textarea {
      width: 100%;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: var(--paper-warm);
      color: var(--ink);
      padding: 0.9rem 1rem;
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-family: var(--font-sans);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      line-height: 1.5;
      transition:
        border-color var(--transition),
        box-shadow var(--transition);
    }

    .contact-field input:focus,
    .contact-field textarea:focus {
      outline: none;
      border-color: var(--accent);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px var(--accent-dim);
    }

    .contact-field textarea {
      min-height: 180px;
      resize: vertical;
    }

    .contact-note {
      font-family: var(--font-sans);
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      color: var(--ink-muted);
      margin: 0;
    }

    .contact-submit {
      justify-self: start;
      border: 0;
      background: var(--ink);
      color: var(--paper);
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 0.8rem 1.2rem;
      font-family: var(--font-sans);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition:
        background var(--transition),
        transform var(--transition);
    }

    .contact-submit:hover {
      background: var(--accent);
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .contact-row {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>

  <p>
    This is <strong>Thinking Hard / Hardly Thinking</strong> — a stack of ideas that
    exists somewhere close to a public notebook with intent to avoid slop. Most of
    the articles, will exist as living docs that will keep on evolving, with time
    and inputs, and changes tracked on git. I am sure that most of the posts will
    only start as semi-polished drafts. Not every argument will be airtight. But everything
    here is written because it felt worth saying out loud.
  </p>

  <p>
    There is no grand story behind how I landed on this name. I was washing
    dishes, and just muttered to my wife - "You know what, Thinking Hard /
    Hardly Thinking seems like a good name for blog". She agreed. Thinking hard
    part of the name is about giving deep thought to the subject, and the Hardly
    Thinking part represents the margins of the idea that often gets overlooked.
  </p>

  <p>
    Topics might include whatever I'm reading, researching, or confused about —
    and I expect that range to wander. Order should might present itself
    naturally.
  </p>

  <hr />

  <p class="contact-intro">
    If you found something worth responding to, I'd genuinely like to hear from
    you.
  </p>

  <form
    class="contact-form"
    action="https://formspree.io/f/xnjozavk"
    method="POST"
  >
    <input type="hidden" name="_subject" value="New message from THHT" />

    <div class="contact-row">
      <div class="contact-field">
        <label for="name">Name</label>
        <input id="name" name="name" type="text" autocomplete="name" required />
      </div>

      <div class="contact-field">
        <label for="email">Email</label>
        <input
          id="email"
          name="email"
          type="email"
          autocomplete="email"
          required
        />
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="contact-field">
      <label for="topic">What is this about?</label>
      <input
        id="topic"
        name="topic"
        type="text"
        placeholder="A post, an idea, a correction, a question..."
      />
    </div>

    <div class="contact-field">
      <label for="message">Message</label>
      <textarea
        id="message"
        name="message"
        placeholder="Write whatever felt worth sending."
        required></textarea>
    </div>

    <p class="contact-note">
      This form sends through Formspree. Include your email if you'd like a
      reply.
    </p>

    <button class="contact-submit" type="submit">Send message</button>
  </form>
</Layout>
